"_ _5"></span>来对待万事</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc7 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">万物、<span class="_ _6"></span>生命现象、<span class="_ _d"></span>宇宙世界等。<span class="_ _6"></span>若能如此，<span class="_ _d"></span>每个人今生中会</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y61 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了知取舍，来世也会非常快乐！ </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
